1 b. The disciplinary action was for the possession or sale of an alcoholic
2 beverage or an illegal controlled substance on school property, and the
3 student subsequently attended and successfully completed, as defined
4 by the applicable State entity, a drug or alcohol treatment counseling
5 program, as appropriate."
