7 PART II. CONFORMING CHANGES
8 SECTION 2. The following statutes are repealed:
9 (1) G.S. 20-9(b1).
10 (2) G.S. 20-13.2(c1).
11 (3) G.S. 115C-12(28).
12 (4) G.S. 115C-150.12C(19).
13 (5) G.S. 115C-218.70.
14 (6) G.S. 115C-238.66(8).
15 (7) G.S. 115C-288(k).
16 (8) G.S. 115C-566.
17
18 PART III. EFFECTIVE DATE
19 SECTION 3. This act becomes effective October 1, 2025, and applies to permit or
20 provisional license applications submitted on or after that date.
